Sec. 33-284.89. Zoning relief from certain requirements.
Relief from the following requirements of this article shall be permitted only pursuant to the standards and requirements of(A)(4)(a) of this code:
Minimum and maximum densities;
Required liner buildings used to screen parking;
Colonnade regulations, including minimum horizontal and vertical clearances;
Provision of A streets;
Requirements for street trees, greens, plazas, squares and medians;
Maximum size of blocks;
Curb requirement in the Core and Center sub-district; and
Signage.
